{"tid":92242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]阿媽着紅裙褂 開房勒死4歲仔","createTime":"2017-01-23T12:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T13:28:29.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6552280611c5a5ba85770324a2e1d813e249c4","tid":92242,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170123/56212633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170123%2F56212633&d=xbL%2BtSzMZHnQbIUZIGsyPnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ebbd2c09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170123%2F56212633&h=dfe64874\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170123/56212633</a><br />\n<br />\n福建惠安縣螺城一酒店，警方昨晚7時許接報發生兇殺案。 一名31歲陳姓女子，穿着中式紅裙褂，將4歲兒子勒死。陳女本來想自殺但沒有勇氣，殺人原因疑與丈夫發生爭吵有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日發出的通報指，醫護人員到酒店客房發現男童已無生命迹象，而女子則處處於醉酒不省人事狀態。警方隨後將陳女帶離醒酒，並展開調查。陳女供稱，因為情所困，萌生了殺死兒子後自殺的念頭，在喝了大量酒後，將兒子張X杰勒死，後因酒力發作，自殺未遂。目前，陳女因涉嫌故意殺人，被警方刑事拘留。案件正在進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43cb15a467e9718d1be96ced8d6a287319fd177","tid":92242,"uid":32877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁猛"},{"pid":"320dfa15e8cd28ab6638f003b6aefce655c77dfe","tid":92242,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"本來兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc315ed9db5bd19d7a7c192cedec41c68b7415c4","tid":92242,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:27:1